Release 0.1.0:
* finish Display API
* finish X11 API implementation
* create Mouse/Keyboard API (hooks and get functions)
* port Construo to the new Display/Input API
* add autoconf/automake support, can be pretty minimal
* make sure that 'make install' works, add some more docs

Release 0.2.0:
* Create GUI (simple buttons)
* make every key bound function accessible via the GUI


Release 0.3.0:
* make OpenGL display implementation, add alpha support (can be faked
  by fading to black on non-alpha displays)
* port to windows
